<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="exercise-n">exercise <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'eksəsaɪz/    美 /'eksərsaɪz/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u">1.★ <strong>[U] 锻炼；运动：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I don't <strong>get</strong> much <strong>exercise</strong> sitting in the office all day.
我整天坐在办公室，很少运动。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The doctor advised him to <strong>take / do</strong> more <strong>exercise</strong>.
医生建议他多运动。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c">2.★ <strong>[C] (一套) 动作；体操：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>morning / stretching exercises 
早操/伸展运动</p></div>

<h4 id="3-c">3.★ <strong>[C] 练习；训练：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>vocabulary / military exercises
词汇练习/军事演习</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Do the exercises on page fifty. 
做第50页的练习。</p></div></div>